  "message": "fix(gateway): fix redaction bugs and misleading documentation\n\n- Fix SENSITIVE_KEYS to use all lowercase (was missing privatekey,\n  accesstoken, refreshtoken, sessionid due to case mismatch)\n- Add additional sensitive keys: bearer, session, cookie\n- Fix misleading UUID v7 comment (actually uses UUID v4)\n- Fix incorrect comment about health endpoint being exempt from logging\n- Add pino-pretty as dev dependency (was used but not installed)\n- Add test for camelCase and snake_case key variants\n\nCo-Authored-By: Claude Opus 4.5 <noreply@anthropic.com>",
